item.title: Why is it giving me an error? 317 PI
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

So it can’t find the folder “src\server\model\players\content”
If you use a compiler.bat, you need to manually add the folder to be compiled. If you use eclipse or an IDE, you’ll be fine otherwise.
As for the other errors, I assume these are items found in the imported file?
